      <h4>Bottom Lid Speaking</h4>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Min cutoff:</strong> 0.10 (barely open)</li>
        <li><strong>Max cutoff:</strong> 0.35 (fully open)</li>
        <li><strong>Volume scale:</strong> 0.25 (sensitivity)</li>
      </ul>
      <h4>Smoothing</h4>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Attack:</strong> 0.25 (fast response)</li>
        <li><strong>Release:</strong> 0.12 (slow decay)</li>
